<br>
Back in the day, before the new graphics engine that gave halfling females plate pants, they used to wear long skirts. My little halfling, decked out in black armor, looked like she was wearing an evening gown...and carrrying a big-ass two-handed sword. *That* was stylish. My barbie is very functional, but he will never be that stylish.<br>
<br>
