<br>
Shorter races also get better innate resists. With the casters now chain casting at aggro, at the lower levels you can get chained to death pretty fast.<br>
<br>
At high end, this doesn't make any difference and even at the lower levels, 2 or 3 pieces of resist gear completely make up the difference.<br>
<br>
