On the subject matter at hand.<br>
Don't debate AC, stats, attributes and all that.<br>
This game, levels mean everything and anything that give you a significant leg-up on levelling is a gigantic plus. <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Go Halfling</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->! That sweet 5% bonus means a lot especially in comparison with the 20% penalty of the Iksars and Trolls (the regen as warriors means little after L50 IMO).   <p><hr />
